      "### How Shorts Get Distributed",
      "When you publish a Short, YouTube initially shows it to a small test audience. If the engagement metrics are strong, the algorithm progressively expands its distribution. This means that even channels with zero subscribers can potentially reach millions of viewers if the content resonates.",
