      "## 2. Craft Click-Worthy Titles",
      "Your title should include your primary keyword, preferably near the beginning. Keep titles under 60 characters to avoid truncation. Make them specific and compelling — a title like 'YouTube SEO: 15 Proven Tips for 2026' is more clickable than 'SEO Tips for YouTube Videos.'",
